        Constructor to initialise the Applicant object with common attributes.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the applicant.
        userId - The unique identifier for the applicant.
        password - The password for the applicant.
        age - The age of the applicant.
        maritalStatus - The marital status of the applicant (e.g., "Single", "Married").
        userType - The type of user (e.g., UserType.APPLICANT).

      • submitApplication

        public void submitApplication​(BTOProject project,
                              FlatType flatType)
                       throws IllegalStateException
        Submit an application for a BTO project. Assumes that the application has been validated and is ready for submission.
        Parameters:
        project - The BTOProject object representing the project to apply for.
        flatType - The FlatType object representing the type of flat to apply for.
        Throws:
        IllegalStateException - if the applicant does not meet the requirements for the specified flat type.
